<h2>Order Confirmation</h2>
<p>Dear <n:invisible n:data="customer_first_name" n:render="data">(First Name)</n:invisible>,</p>

<p>Thank you for making an enquiry about a photo at www.into-the-light.com. Here is your enquiry confirmation. At the moment I am only able to check enquiries once every few days. I hope to get back to people in at least a week.</p>

<hr />  
  
  <h2>Enquiry Details</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><td>Enquiry Number</td><td n:data="order_num" n:render="data">(Order Number)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Enquiry Date</td><td n:data="create_date" n:render="data">(Create Date)</td></tr>
  </table>

<hr />
  <h2>Basket</h2>
  <table >
    <tr >
      <th style="text-align: left">Description</th>
      <th>Unit Price</th>
      <th>Quantity</th>
      <th>Price</th>
    </tr>
    <n:invisible n:data="items" n:render="sequence">
      <tr n:pattern="item" n:render="basket_item">
        <td><n:slot name="description" /></td>
        <td>&pound;<n:slot name="unit_price" /></td>
        <td><n:slot name="quantity_ordered" /></td>
        <td>&pound;<n:slot name="total_price" /></td>
      </tr>
    </n:invisible>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="3">Total Price</td>
      <td>&pound;<n:invisible n:data="total_price" n:render="data">(Total Price)</n:invisible></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
<hr />

<p>Yours Sincerely</p>



<p>David Ward <br />
